Feature: Logging into Demo Web Shop Application

@ValidCredentials
  Scenario: testing login with valid credentials
  Given launching the page DemoShop
  When click the log in
    And given the valid email for login
    And given the valid password for login
    And click the login in login page
    Then login was successfull
   
 
  @InvalidCredentials
  Scenario: testing login with Invalid credentials
    Given launching the page DemoShop
    When click the log in
    And given the Invalid email for login
    And given the Invalid password for login
    And click the login button in login page
    Then login was unsuccessf